    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s pinnacle naturally aspirated engineering. Powered by the S54 3.2L inline-six, the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated VANOS system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers tactile gear engagement, paired with a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common structural fatigue. While showing minor aesthetic wear consistent with its age, the vehicle's kinematics and powertrain performance remain sharp, offering the visceral feedback and balanced weight distribution sought by purists.",
